V449

Release Date: 2025-11-27

Bug Fixes & Improvements:

1. Fixed Q Skill Cooldown Display Visibility Issue
   - Fixed cooldown circle disappearing when ready (opacity 0 -> 0.5)
   - Changed position from absolute to fixed for better visibility
   - Added z-index 400 to prevent overlay issues
   - Added runtime protection and safety checks
   - Added safe-area-inset support for notched phones

2. Fixed FBX Animation File Names for R2 CDN Loading
   - Fixed Animation_Run_60.fbx to Animation_RunFast_frame_rate_60.fbx
   - Fixed Animation_Death_60.fbx to Animation_Dead_frame_rate_60.fbx
   - Added improved error handling and loading progress logs

3. Network Latency Optimizations
   - Enabled instant client-side prediction for movement
   - Optimized server state synchronization
   - Enabled local collision detection in multiplayer mode

Previous Version (V424):
- Comprehensive Movement & Collision Fixes
- Fixed remaining stuttering, knife collision failures, and latency-related jitter
